CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 14, 1954, pg. 3 reads: "At Omegas' Picnic - Pittsburgh's chapters of Omega Psi Phi Fraternity held their annual picnic at North Park Lodge Tuesday afternoon and evening and, of course, there were plenty of ladies on hand to help the Omegas celebrate...The Courier photographer snapped the two visitors in the center picture. They are Mrs. Marie C. Giles of Chase City, Va., and Miss Loretta Rucker of New York, N.Y..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Marie C. Giles and Loretta Rucker, standing in front of a stone wall in North Park Lodge for Omega Psi Phi annual picnic
